---


import Card from '../ui/Card.astro';
---

<!-- <SectionWrapper --> <section className="bg-white py-20 border-b border-slate-100">
  <!-- <ContentContainer> --> <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
        Proof Should Show the Full Learning System, Not Just Screenshots
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
        A strong online learning project is not only a page design. It includes course strategy, content structure, learner flow, platform setup, funnels, automations, student onboarding, QA, and support after launch.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">

      <Card className="flex flex-col h-full bg-slate-50 border-slate-200">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#EFF6FF] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#27496D]">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 18v-5.25m0 0a6.01 6.01 0 001.5-.189m-1.5.189a6.01 6.01 0 01-1.5-.189m3.75 7.478a12.06 12.06 0 01-4.5 0m3.75 2.383a14.406 14.406 0 01-3 0M14.25 18v-.192c0-.983.658-1.82 1.508-2.316a7.5 7.5 0 10-7.516 0c.85.496 1.508 1.333 1.508 2.316V18" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Strategy Before Design</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm flex-grow">
          We define the learner journey and map out the entire educational experience before touching any platform tools or templates.
        </p>
      </Card>

      <Card className="flex flex-col h-full bg-slate-50 border-slate-200">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#EFF6FF] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#27496D]">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 12h16.5m-16.5 3.75h16.5M3.75 19.5h16.5M5.625 4.5h12.75a1.875 1.875 0 010 3.75H5.625a1.875 1.875 0 010-3.75z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Learning Structure First</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm flex-grow">
          Modules, lessons, and resources are organized for clarity and progression before uploading to a platform or LMS.
        </p>
      </Card>

      <Card className="flex flex-col h-full bg-slate-50 border-slate-200">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#EFF6FF] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#27496D]">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Student Experience</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm flex-grow">
          We prioritize clear onboarding, intuitive navigation, and automated communication over surface-level decoration.
        </p>
      </Card>

      <Card className="flex flex-col h-full bg-slate-50 border-slate-200">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#EFF6FF] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#27496D]">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Launch & Support</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm flex-grow">
          A project is not finished at build. We provide QA checklists, pre-launch testing, and ongoing support systems after the launch.
        </p>
      </Card>

    </div>
  </div> <!-- </ContentContainer> -->
</section> <!-- </SectionWrapper> -->
